    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Domini. Anno ab incarnatjone Domini millesimo septuagesimo quinto,
                        regnante vero <persName key="#Emperor/king" ref="#people/77"
                            >Heinrico</persName> filio quondam Einritj inperatoris anno viesimo, die
                        sextodetjmo mensis novembris, inditjone quartadetjma, <placeName
                            ref="#places/594">Ravenne</placeName>. Peto a te in Dei nomine <persName
                            key="#Priors" ref="#people/1598">Marco</persName> venerabile <rs
                            key="#Priors">priore</rs>
                        <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterii</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Landed_possessions #Penalty #Wine #Fruits/vegetables #Rent_in_money #Monasteries"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1460">Sancte Marie in <placeName
                                ref="#places/4179">Pomposea</placeName></orgName>, ex iussione
                            <persName key="#Abbots" ref="#people/4300">Uberti</persName> venerabili
                            <rs key="#Abbots">abbatis</rs> adfirmandam eam cum consensu monachorum
                        eiusdem monasterii, uti michi presenti in Christi nomine <persName><name
                                ref="Petrus de Hugone">Petro de Ugone</name></persName> petitori pro
                        me et pro meis filiis tantum per <rs key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis"
                            >enfiteuticarium ius</rs> a presenti die concedisti mihi et largisti seu
                        confirmasti rem iuris prefati monasterii, idest omnes res vestras inmobiles
                        quas vos habetis et detinetis vel que vobis pertinent in <placeName
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Landed_possessions
                            #Wine #Fruits/vegetables"
                            ref="#places/4622">Luibola</placeName>, cum <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">terris</rs>, <rs key="#Wine">vineis</rs>,
                            <rs>salectis</rs>, <rs key="#Landed_possessions">satjonalibus</rs>,
                            <rs>arbustis</rs>, <rs key="#Fruits/vegetables">arboribus</rs> et cum
                        omnibus sibi pertinentibus. Que res quondam venerunt a <persName><name
                                ref="Fedrona">Fedrona</name></persName> et ab <persName ref="#Judge"
                                ><name ref="Ungarus">Ungaro</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudice</rs>, que res detinentur a <persName><name
                                ref="Petrus de Pitallo">Petro de Pitallo</name></persName> cum suis
                        consortibus et a <persName><name ref="Leo de Paulo">Leone de
                            Paulo</name></persName> cum suis consortibus, habendas, tenendas,
                        defensandas et in omnibus meliorandas, sub pensione <rs key="#Rent_in_money"
                            >denariorum Veneticorum duodetjm</rs> tantum omni martjo mense aut infra
                        inditjonem pro predictis omnibus rebus. Pro eo quia vos accepistis,
                        caltjarii nomine, idest restitutjonem terrarum et vinearum quas detinui a
                        iure monasterii vestri, quas res restituo vobis per concanbium. Ita et post
                        transitum meum meorumque filiorum munimine expleto quando Domino placuerit,
                        tunc predicte res culte, laborate et in omnibus meliorate vel quicquid a
                        nobis inibi additum melioratumque fuerit ad ius dominiumque predicti
                        monasterii vestri, cuius est ius et proprietas, modis omnibus revertantur,
                        sub pene nomine <rs key="#Penalty">auri dimidiam libram</rs>, spondens et
                        maneat firma hec enfiteosim. Ego <persName key="#Tabellio"><name
                                ref="Petrus"> Petrus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Tabellio">tabellio</rs> scripsi hanc aperem.</ab>
